    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/00ea474f10805c81caad3abd876951a3.avif?t=1758162796\" width=1560 height=439 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fight to Survive in the Grim Dark world of <strong>We The People</strong>, an <strong>FPSMMO</strong> where you can choose between <strong>PvPvE</strong> or <strong>PvE</strong>. Play as either a <strong>Core</strong> or <strong>Hardcore</strong> character and engage with various Factions, all vying for power and control with their own intentions and motivations. <strong>WTP</strong> focuses on <strong>realism, immersion, tactical gameplay, and horror</strong>. Blending the <strong>high skill ceiling</strong> of Tactical Shooters, with the <strong>high-risk, high-reward</strong> of Extraction Shooters, our goal is to provide a truly <strong>unforgiving experience</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SQUAD UP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/d434cfcfab8d95687baaa2631f6c428f.poster.avif?t=1758162796\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/d434cfcfab8d95687baaa2631f6c428f.webm?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/d434cfcfab8d95687baaa2631f6c428f.mp4?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you <strong>Deploy</strong> into a <strong>Raid</strong>, expect a <strong>unique</strong> outcome. <strong>Stake</strong> your gear, and <strong>risk it all</strong> with Squads up to <strong>5 Players</strong>, engage in <strong>Tactical</strong> and <strong>Coordinated</strong> gameplay in order to <strong>Loot. Shoot. Survive. </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GRIM DARK WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/1237c733c40205bcaddf89f0bfe52c42.poster.avif?t=1758162796\" width=606 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/1237c733c40205bcaddf89f0bfe52c42.webm?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/1237c733c40205bcaddf89f0bfe52c42.mp4?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the <strong><i>BEAUTIFUL</i></strong> Pacific Northwest. Experience a fictional <strong>Dystopian</strong> take on this <strong>breathtaking</strong> and <strong>bone-chilling</strong> part of the <strong>United States</strong>. With a <strong>Dynamic Weather System</strong>, and bespoke<strong> Environments</strong>, be prepared to experience the <strong>PNW</strong> like never before.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNFORGIVING REALISM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/6acbb01a9e4e1587a587401c77600c11.poster.avif?t=1758162796\" width=606 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/6acbb01a9e4e1587a587401c77600c11.webm?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/6acbb01a9e4e1587a587401c77600c11.mp4?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Death</strong> means losing <strong>all</strong> of your hard earned <strong>Loot</strong>. So, managing the <strong>Hydration</strong> and <strong>Starvation</strong> system along with our <strong>Tactical Combat</strong> system, <strong>Advanced Medical</strong> systems and <strong>Immersive Movement</strong>-Surviving the <strong>Elements, Wildlife, Enemy Factions, Zombies, and Players</strong> will be your biggest priority.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNBRIDLED CUSTOMIZATION</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/52ef0a5b44dc33ccc18814c409e4b50c.poster.avif?t=1758162796\" width=606 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/52ef0a5b44dc33ccc18814c409e4b50c.webm?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/52ef0a5b44dc33ccc18814c409e4b50c.mp4?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WTP</strong> offers a robust <strong>Firearm Customization</strong> system that provides a near-countless number of possible options for Players to choose from. Create your dream kit,  or steal someone else's-either way, enjoy realistic weapons, equipment, and gear all with unique stats-that will allow you to better survive the unknown.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BRUTAL &amp; MATURE STORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/b4859257ce74b0361decf7ab6011bdae.poster.avif?t=1758162796\" width=606 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/b4859257ce74b0361decf7ab6011bdae.webm?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/b4859257ce74b0361decf7ab6011bdae.mp4?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and uncover the truth of a <strong>Mysterious</strong> and <strong>Broken</strong> world, filled with unique story elements and an abundance of <strong>hidden secrets</strong>. Traverse through <strong>sprawling forests, urban, residential, and industrial locations, including underground bunkers, nuclear facilities, and devastated cityscapes</strong> to discover what the <strong>Brutal</strong> world of <strong>WTP</strong> has to offer.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WIPE BASED PROGRESSION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/a9ebc58ed48cddf4258ef5a7fdb8442c.poster.avif?t=1758162796\" width=606 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/a9ebc58ed48cddf4258ef5a7fdb8442c.webm?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2261560/extras/a9ebc58ed48cddf4258ef5a7fdb8442c.mp4?t=1758162796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete<strong> Quests</strong>, <strong>Stash Loot</strong>, or engage in <strong>Commerce</strong> with your fellow Survivors. Amass an <strong>Arsenal</strong> of <strong>Weapons</strong>, <strong>Equipment</strong>, and <strong>Items</strong> necessary to take on the many looming threats that await you.</p>",
